title: Apartment for Rent
description: This spacious apartment is located in the Scheldebuurt neighborhood of Amsterdam. It features a modern design and includes amenities such as a supermarket and bus stop nearby. The apartment is available for rent and is offered with an indefinite lease agreement. It has a monthly rent price of €1,600 (excluding service costs of €32.00/month). The apartment will be available starting from August 23, 2023. Viewings can be arranged upon request. No security deposit is required. Please visit the provided link for more details and to schedule a viewing.

importantInformation.viewings: Viewings can be arranged upon request.
